the operators and an addition

00:52:16.112 --> 00:52:18.070
on the coefficients in
the way I've written it.

00:52:22.250 --> 00:52:24.550
So that's just a
rearrangement of the physics.

00:52:24.550 --> 00:52:31.980
And we've set it up so that the
