changing the thing,

00:53:02.300 --> 00:53:05.740
the definitions here, but I have
now the freedom to pick these

00:53:05.740 --> 00:53:06.410
d's.

00:53:06.410 --> 00:53:08.035
And what I can do is
I can pick the d's

00:53:08.035 --> 00:53:11.350
to have the same renormalon
as the MS-bar scheme.

00:53:11.350 --> 00:53:13.960
And, therefore, I can
iteratively, again,

00:53:13.960 --> 00:53:17.400
remove the first
problematic term of this

00:53:17.400 --> 00:53:22.300
to get a better
