00:59:06.090 --> 00:59:12.180
Anyway, OK, so you can
again, after you've

00:59:12.180 --> 00:59:15.600
got this definition, you
could actually formally write

00:59:15.600 --> 00:59:20.760
this as C0 bar [INAUDIBLE] Q, mu
