01:18:31.010 --> 01:18:33.560
And you can understand what's
going on with that fine tuning

01:18:33.560 --> 01:18:36.693
and actually propagate it to
change your power counting,

01:18:36.693 --> 01:18:38.110
to change your
power counting such

01:18:38.110 --> 01:18:41.165
that it takes into account the
existence of that fine tuning.

01:18:41.165 --> 01:18:44.060
It builds the whole effective
theory around the idea

01:18:44.060 --> 01:18:47.480
that there was this fine
tuning from original, perhaps,

01:18:47.480 --> 01:18:49.490
dimension counting
point of view.

01:18:49.490 --> 01:18:51.680
But we can adopt a
different power counting

01:18:51.680 --> 01:18:54.590
that actually organizes
the physics in exactly

01:18:54.590 --> 01:18:56.017
the right way that we want to.

01:18:56.017 --> 01:18:58.350
