01:19:18.560 --> 01:19:24.080
would be very difficult if we
weren't using effective field

01:19:24.080 --> 01:19:25.790
theory along the way.

01:19:30.423 --> 01:19:32.090
So we'll investigate
an effective theory

01:19:32.090 --> 01:19:37.640
that has a naively
irrelevant operator that must

01:19:37.640 --> 01:19:40.600
be promoted to being relevant.

01:19:48.150 --> 01:19:50.800
So by dimensional analysis,
it would be irrelevant.

01:19:50.800 --> 01:19:52.800
And one way of thinking
about it is that it just

01:19:52.800 --> 01:19:55.140
has such a large anomalous
dimension that it actually

01:19:55.140 --> 01:19:57.870
ends up being totally relevant.

01:19:57.870 --> 01:20:02.110
And that is actually not a
bad way of thinking about it.

01:20:02.110 --> 01:20:05.400
So the example
