are integrated out.

01:21:01.190 --> 01:21:03.500
So there's nothing to
exchange and really just have

01:21:03.500 --> 01:21:06.090
contact type interactions.

01:21:06.090 --> 01:21:08.450
So something that you might
think of as like A pion

01:21:08.450 --> 01:21:12.890
exchange between
two nucleons gets

01:21:12.890 --> 01:21:16.650
represented by some local
operators between the nucleons.

